General.Name: Great Boulder Resources Ltd
General.Description: Great Boulder Resources Limited operates as a mineral exploration company in Australia. The company primarily explores for gold and base metals. Its flagship project is the Side Well Gold Project consisting of a single tenement covering approximately 132 square kilometers located in the Meekatharra in Western Australia. Great Boulder Resources Limited was incorporated in 2016 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
